race.comment: DIFENSIVO (6) progressive gelding who got off the mark at start five with a a tough on-speed win over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Finds a winnable contest from the right gate. Go close. BETHSHEBA (11) back in grade on resumption with a gritty on-pace second over 1000m at Port Macquarie. Returned a good set of figures on that occasion and looks to have returned well. Respect. BRAZEN BRANDO (13) improved sharply in the rain affected going with a commanding victory over 1000m at Tuncurry. Gets weight relief and hard to ignore in his current form. Each way. SAPPHIRE KISS (3) improved sharply from the wide gate when she finished over the top of them to score a nose win over this track and trip. Similar set-up again and stays in the mix.
